data.name: strParrafo1
data.value: In Skytex we are proud to be one of the most important manufacturers in the region of the Free Trade Agreement of North America and Latin America fabric polyester high torque, as well as synthetic fabrics with spandex circular dyed and printed fabric.

data.name: strParrafo10

data.name: strParrafo11
data.value: Group is composed of Skytex Skytex company dedicated to the manufacture of woven fabrics and knitted produced with synthetic and artificial fibers of high quality. Skyfelt specialized in the manufacture of non-woven felts. Skymatt manufacturer of regenerated fibers and nonwoven products for the mattress industry, furniture and automotive industries. Its facilities are located in Huejotzingo Industrial Park, in the heart of Puebla and cover more than 80,000 square meters

data.name: strParrafo12
data.value: In Skytex we are convinced of the fundamental role that meets cutting edge technology to adequately meet the demand of markets in a global economy. Therefore, we intend to have the technology and the most modern equipment available in the world, such as those used to design digital systems, engraving, woven and printed fabrics as well as the most advanced control systems of production They allow you to monitor each of the steps of the entire manufacturing processes.

data.name: strParrafo13
data.value: Today, intensive and appropriate use of technology has allowed us to have highly controlled processes through fully computerized systems, thanks to which we can permanently guarantee the superior quality of our fabrics.

data.name: strParrafo14
data.value: Always offer superior quality in all our prodcutos is the goal and commitment established with our customers. To fulfill this, we have a specialized barcode system that monitors and evaluates all processes in order to ensure compliance with the highest standards of international quality.

data.name: strParrafo15
data.value: Each of our inputs and raw materials, yarns, dyes and chemicals, etc., as well as the final products are subject to rigorous inspection using the most technologically advanced equipment, controlling them compliance with specifications that enable us to guarantee complete satisfaction of our customers.

data.name: strParrafo16
data.value: In addition to our rigorous production controls we have a monitoring system that allows us to track customer orders to ensure timely delivery of our products.

data.name: strParrafo17
data.value: The geographical location of the facilities Skytex complements the facilities for the provision of a service of excellence. Our location in the downtown area of Mexico translates into shorter and ease distances of communication with our customers and suppliers to thereby make the flow of inputs and raw materials required in our production processes more efficient as well as our products finished. Also, being of NAFTA origin, our products enjoy preferential conditions to export to the United States, Canada and Europe.

data.name: strParrafo18
data.value: We are a company that fulfills an active role in favor of technology. Not only do we comply with government regulations in the field of industry, but also going beyond local specifications to meet our own objectives and programs on ecological matters.

data.name: strParrafo19
data.value: We have a plant for the biological treatment of water, its recycling and reuse in our production processes. We have a system of collecting rainwater that allows us to store, treat and reuse water 12,000 m2. Recover the condensed steam to save energy in our processes, and of course, comply with all regulations on emissions and waste treatment.

data.name: strParrafo2
data.value: Due to its equipment and advanced technology, our plant well be considered one of the most modern of its kind worldwide.

data.name: strParrafo20
